Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}能够帮助我们  帮助人类\Nsomething that could help us, help humanity.
