Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你也知道  我们很需要走一回运了\NI mean, you know damn well we could use a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或许这就是撞大运了呢\NWhat if we finally got one?
