Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}找到了\NGottenyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这本书  我们得保护好它\NThis book -- we need to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个跟着我的东西  他太接近了\NThis thing they put on me -- he's too close!
