Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.39,0:28:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让亚伦下令是什么意思\Nwhen -- when you tell Aaron to take charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.62,0:28:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那小子如果查了资料  他就会知道\NThe boy would know... if he could consult the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.23,0:29:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}资料  什么资料\NPages? W-what pages?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.69,0:29:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在我...在我行受戒礼的时候\NWhen I was -- when I was bar mitzvahed,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.94,0:29:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我祖父给了我一本薄薄的旧书\Nmy -- my grandfather gave me this little old book.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.15,0:29:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是希伯来语写的\NIt was in hebrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.17,0:29:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}算是泥人的使用手册\NIt was like an owner's manual for a golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.85,0:29:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很好  那就学啊\NOkay. Great. Get that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.52,0:29:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可我没能...\NI I can't...exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.83,0:29:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我上了中学  有点玩世不恭\NWhen I went to high school, I sort of...drifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.62,0:29:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没心思学习\NI started getting off the academic track,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.35,0:29:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}于是我就...\Nand, uh, I kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.79,0:29:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就卷起来点了\N...I kind of smoked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.12,0:29:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小子用书页卷了烟\NThe boy smoked the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.45,0:29:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那纸张只有这么薄  牛皮纸\NThey were these thin, vellum-y pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.04,0:29:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}卷烟是再合适不过了\NI-I mean, it was perfect for rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.30,0:29:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  几张破纸就能操纵泥巴人\NLook, they were driving instructions for a clay man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.73,0:29:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这不是荒唐吗\NOkay? It was nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.10,0:29:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吗  我是说\NRight? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.94,0:30:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.43,0:30:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  我很抱歉  行了吧\NOkay. All right. Look, I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.20,0:30:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有什么需要我学的  你告诉我不就行了\NWhy can't you just tell me what I don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.43,0:30:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没有资格指导拉比\NIt's not my place to guide the rabbi,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.08,0:30:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}教授教师\Nto teach the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.76,0:30:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这不是我的责任\NIt's not my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.80,0:30:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}接管\NYifalchunbee!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.46,0:30:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个  确实让人不怎么舒服\NThat's not super-comforting, got to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.03,0:30:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只能说  那些实验\NSo as far as I can tell, these experiments --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.08,0:30:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}修黎社残杀犹太人  吉普赛人\Nthe thule were murdering Jews, Gypsies --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.67,0:30:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}基本上没人能幸免\NJust about anybody and everybody --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.22,0:30:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后用魔法使他们复活\Nthen trying to magically reanimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.27,0:30:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们企图找到方法\NThey were trying to figure out a way
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.00,0:30:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让死去的自己人复活\Nto bring their own dead back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.60,0:30:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我估计他们最后成功了\NWhich I'm guessing they figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.56,0:30:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为这个\Nbecause -- this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.14,0:30:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最后一页\NThis last page...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.51,0:30:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所有死而复生的修黎社人的名册\NIs a roster of every dead thule member who was reanimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.30,0:31:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们就因此杀了我祖父\NThis is why they killed my grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.70,0:31:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上面写了怎么干掉他们吗\NAnything in there on how to kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.06,0:31:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很明显他们做了这样的实验\NApparently, they experimented with that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.43,0:31:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}爆头\NHeadshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.88,0:31:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但如果十二个小时内没有烧掉尸体\NBut if you don't burn the body within 12 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.41,0:31:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就会复活\Nit reanimates again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.77,0:31:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}混账纳粹\NNazi bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.91,0:32:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}摄像头记录全部被销毁了\NThe security camera's hard drives have all been wiped.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.16,0:32:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你确定他被干掉了吗\NAre you sure he's been murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.67,0:32:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}托瓦兹死在这里\NTorvald was killed here,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.60,0:32:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但杀手不是人类\Nbut not by a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.56,0:32:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我本可以知道更多  可他的魂魄没来得及说\NI'd know more, but his ghost was forced to depart
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.91,0:32:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就被迫离开了\Nbefore it could tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.44,0:32:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们清楚要烧掉尸体\NThey knew enough to burn his remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.06,0:32:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是血吗\NBlood?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.99,0:32:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}泥土\NClay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.04,0:33:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}托瓦兹杀死了计划的最后一个拉比\NTorvald kills the initiative's last rabbi,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.25,0:33:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如今维台普斯克的泥人杀死了他\Nand now the golem of Vitsyebsk kills him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.25,0:33:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  盖思  不是工具社会\NNo, no, Garth, not a tool society --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.58,0:33:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是修黎社\N"Thule" -- t-h-u-l-e.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.17,0:33:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.79,0:33:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好  有发现就联系我\NAll right. Call me if you find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.65,0:33:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}盖思的所有线人都没辙\NAll of Garth's contacts are stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.73,0:33:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}根本就没人听说过\NNobody on the circuit's ever even heard
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.97,0:33:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"修黎社"\Nof "The Thule Society"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.31,0:33:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论是些什么人\NWhoever these people are,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.02,0:33:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们藏得够深\Nthey've been flying beneath the hunter radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.28,0:33:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有发现吗\NAnything?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.14,0:33:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没什么靠谱的\NNothing solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.22,0:33:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}相关的传说倒是不少\NI mean, the lore is all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.56,0:33:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有个说法是  只要擦去其前额的一个字母\NUh, according to one legend, um, it can be shut down
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.76,0:33:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就可以让其停止行动\Nif you erase one of the letters off its forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.61,0:33:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-那张泥巴脸上没有字母  -的确没有\N- I didn't see any letters on clayface. - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.46,0:33:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不管这个  另一个是说\NSo, side-burner that. Another one --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.45,0:33:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}古代传说  泥人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.79,0:33:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"有的嘴里有卷轴  你要拔出来"\N"Some have a scroll in their mouth you're supposed to rip out."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.26,0:33:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}咬着卷轴还能说清楚话吗\NWouldn't that give him some sort of a lisp or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.05,0:33:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}根据传说  它们根本就不能说话\NWell, classically, they're not even supposed to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.16,0:33:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们都知道  他单枪匹马\NWe do know that he took on an entire camp
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.25,0:33:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}解决了全副武装的德军营地\Nfull of heavily armed german soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.97,0:33:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和修黎社巫师\Nand thule necromancers and won.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.54,0:33:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}虎头虎脑的大坏蛋\NOne badass hummel figurine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.01,0:33:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们完全不知道怎么让它熄火\NThat we have no idea how to put back in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.29,0:33:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好极了\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.59,0:34:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这就是你们的计划\NSo, that's your plan --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.44,0:34:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}解决我的泥人\Ntaking out my Golem?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.38,0:34:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还不是什么计划\NIt's not a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.00,0:34:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只是知道了怎么办  感觉好些  就这样\NWe would just feel a lot better if we knew how. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.98,0:34:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们凭什么以为自己有权做这样的决定\NWhat makes you think you have any right to make that decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.05,0:34:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}相信我\NBelieve me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.70,0:34:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果我们需要  我们就去争取\Nif we need the right, we will take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.77,0:34:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  他也许很讨人厌\NLook, he may be a pain in the ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.94,0:34:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我要对他负责\Nbut he's my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.54,0:34:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}泥人为了战争而创造出来的\NLook, the Golem was built to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.38,0:34:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可没受到这样的训练\NYou're not trained for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.82,0:34:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你打算如何继续下去\NNow, how are you gonna take that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.32,0:34:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.10,0:34:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}住手\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.03,0:34:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}找到你了  残酷无情的怪物\NThere you are, you grim piece of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.17,0:35:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}找你好多年了\Nafter all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.02,0:35:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}艾克哈特\NEckhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.24,0:35:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}亚当之泥  向我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.86,0:35:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以创造者所订立的契约命令你\NI command you by the covenant of your makers --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.91,0:35:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}亚当之泥  向我投降\NClay of Adam, surrender your bond unto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.20,0:35:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是泥人的拉比\NSo, you are the golem's rabbi?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.20,0:35:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你唤醒了他\NYou woke him...
